snippet.title: Heroes of Delum - Trailer Steam Greenlight
snippet.description:
Heroes of Delum - real-time strategy, single and multiplayer co-op game. Play as 1 to 5 friends and survive together!

Free alpha demo: https://delumstudios.itch.io/heroes-of-delum
Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=867787844
Official Website: http://www.heroesofdelum.com/
